   "source": [
    "# 🧪 Python Variables & Strings: The Deep Dive\n",
    "\n",
    "## A. Variable Naming & Unpacking\n",
    "Python sangat fleksibel dalam pengisian nilai. Gunakan `snake_case` untuk nama variabel.\n",
    "- **Multiple Assignment**: `x, y, z = 1, 2, 3`\n",
    "- **Unpacking**: Membongkar isi list ke variabel terpisah."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "# Latihan Unpacking\n",
    "data_user = [\"Budi\", 25, \"Jakarta\"]\n",
    "nama, umur, kota = data_user\n",
    "\n",
    "print(f\"User {nama} tinggal di {kota} dan berumur {umur} tahun.\")"
   ],
   "outputs": [],
   "execution_count": null
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## B. Global Keyword & Scope\n",
    "Variabel di dalam `def` (fungsi) bersifat **Local**. Gunakan keyword `global` jika ingin memodifikasi variabel di luar fungsi."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "poin = 0\n",
    "\n",
    "def tambah_poin():\n",
    "    global poin\n",
    "    poin = poin + 10\n",
    "\n",
    "tambah_poin()\n",
    "print(\"Poin sekarang:\", poin) # Hasilnya harus 10"
   ],
   "outputs": [],
   "execution_count": null
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## C. String Indexing & Slicing\n",
    "Format: `string[start : stop : step]`\n",
    "- `start`: Index awal (ikut diambil).\n",
    "- `stop`: Index akhir (TIDAK ikut diambil).\n",
    "- `step`: Jarak lompatan antar karakter."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "alphabet = \"ABCDEFGHIJKLMNOPQRSTUVWXYZ\"\n",
    "\n",
    "# Ambil karakter ke-10 (Index 9)\n",
    "print(\"Index 9:\", alphabet[9])\n",
    "\n",
    "# Ambil potongan dari index 0 sampai 5 (ABCDE)\n",
    "print(\"Slicing 0-5:\", alphabet[0:5])\n",
    "\n",
    "# Balikkan urutan string (Reverse)\n",
    "print(\"Reverse:\", alphabet[::-1])"
   ],
   "outputs": [],
   "execution_count": null
  },
